dct_title_s: Sketch map of a portion of the Essequebo and Potaro Rivers, showing the position of Kaieteur Fall : to accompany the paper by C. B. Brown, Esqre
dct_description_sm: Waterfalls, escarpments, islands, paths and portages along river, and settlements are shown. Relief shown by hachures. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 41 (1871), pp. 77-100; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.47 1871
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society, by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1871.
